  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of MP-424, Interferon Beta (IFN Beta), and Ribavirin(RBV) in Treatment-Na誰ve or Having Received Interferon Based Therapy With Chronic Hepatitis C (CHC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3 Study of MP-424 in Combination With IFN Beta and RBV, in Subjects With Genotype 1/2 Hepatitis C, Who Are Treatment-Na誰ve or Have Received Interferon Based Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
