  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy and safety of MP-424 with IFN beta and RBV in patients
      with genotype 1/2 hepatitis C, who are treatment-na誰ve or have received its treatment before.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
